org.agreement_technologies.service.map_parser

Class TaskImp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agreement_technologies.service.map_parser.TaskImp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Task

    public class TaskImp
extends java.lang.Object
implements Task
    Implementation of an ungrounded planning task. Stores the problem and domain information of a parsed planning task.
    Since:
    1.0
